docs.text: Tempus Dominus Tempus Dominus is the successor to the very popular to what was "bootstrap-datetimepicker". The plugin provide a robust date and time picker designed to integrate into your project. We're going through some changes right now and the docs will be updated soon. Please be sure to read the blog post linked above. If you are looking for the old docs you can find them here .
